==光缆中断==
*2005年7月，巴基斯坦登陆点卡拉奇以南35千米外的一段光缆发生故障，导致巴基斯坦与国际互联网连接的主要互联通道中断，一千万用户受到影响。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pakistantimes.net/2005/07/06/top5.htm|title=Pakistan Times {{!}} Top Story: Standby Net arrangements terminated in Pakistan|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110213044412/http://pakistantimes.net/2005/07/06/top5.htm|archivedate=2011-02-13|accessdate=2015-07-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/breaking/communication-breakdown-in-pakistan/2005/06/29/1119724673577.html?from=moreStories | work=The Sydney Morning Herald | title=Communication breakdown in Pakistan | date=29 June 2005 | accessdate=2015-07-15 | archive-date=2010-09-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100902150043/http://www.smh.com.au/news/breaking/communication-breakdown-in-pakistan/2005/06/29/1119724673577.html?from=moreStories | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2005-06-28/pakistan/27867464_1_submarine-cable-ptcl-karachi | work=The Times Of India | title=Pakistan cut off from the world | date=28 June 2005 | accessdate=2015-07-15 | archive-date=2014-01-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108042911/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2005-06-28/pakistan/27867464_1_submarine-cable-ptcl-karachi | dead-url=no }}</ref>
*2006年12月26日，怀疑由于[[2006年恆春地震|2006年恆春地震]]影响，包括此光缆的多条光缆中断，远东地区的互联网服务受到严重破坏。据报道，该光缆花费三周时间去进行修复。<ref name="BBC-6213501">{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/6213501.stm | title = Asia phone links start to recover | publisher = BBC News | date = 28 December 2006 | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | archive-date = 2008-12-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081228101602/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/6213501.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>
*2008年1月30日，一艘船只在埃及亚历山大港撞断了作为冗余线路的新光缆[[SEA-ME-WE_4|SEA-ME-WE 4]]，导致从中东和南亚至欧洲和美国的互联网服务严重迟滞，而埃及连接互联网服务的速度损失了70%，但作为印度最大的互联网供应商[[印度国营电信公司|印度国营电信公司]]则表示只对印度10%~15%的用户的互联网服务造成影响。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601085&sid=a3tADKd_tY3g&refer=europe|title=Bloomberg}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>
